// #register udf
// spark.udf.register("get_only_file_name", (fullPath: String) => fullPath.split("/").last)
// spark.udf.register("get_file_name", (path: String) => path.split("/").last.head)

import org.apache.spark.sql.functions.dayofyear

val solar_raw = spark
            .read
            .option("header","true")
            .option("delimiter",",")
            .schema(solar_schema.schema)
            .csv(solar_files3)
            .withColumn("input_file_name", input_file_name())
            .withColumn("zinput_file_name", split($"input_file_name","/").getItem(8))
            .withColumn("USAF", split($"zinput_file_name","_").getItem(0))
            .withColumn("day", dayofyear($"YYYY-MM-DD"))
            .withColumn("hour", split($"HH:MM (LST)",":").getItem(0))
            
// solar_raw.select("USAF").show()

val solar_meta = spark
                .read
                .option("header","true")
                .option("delimiter",",")
                .csv(solar_meta_file)
// solar_meta.show()

val solar = solar_raw.join(solar_meta, "USAF")
                    .select($"day",$"hour".cast("Int"),$"NSRDB_LAT (dd)".cast("Float") as "LAT",$"NSRDB_LON(dd)".cast("Float").alias("LONG"),$"ETR (Wh/m^2)".alias("ETR"))
                    
// val solar = solar_temp.select($"USAF",$"day",$"hour",$"NSRDB_LAT (dd)".alias("LAT"),$"NSRDB_LON(dd)".alias("LONG"),$"ETR (Wh/m^2)".alias("ETR"))
// val solar = solar_raw.withColumn("filename", input_file_name())
solar.cache()
solar.count()

import org.apache.spark.ml.feature.{VectorAssembler, VectorIndexer}

val vectorAssembler = new VectorAssembler().setInputCols(featuresCols).setOutputCol("rawFeatures")

val vectorIndexer = new VectorIndexer().setInputCol("rawFeatures").setOutputCol("features")//.setMaxCategories(4)
